<br>
If you want to solo get 2 things a paladin needs.Tsernnia's whip , and/or wavecrasher.<br>
Tseinna's whip is a 7/22 procs muscle lock 1. Ie a poision based snare.Random duration.<br>
Its great for the grey, use it , proc, switch weapons and  fear kill.<br>
Wont land on vamps in SoL, so ten b and ME are outta luck.Hmm lands on giants in Keal good,and Even landed it on a few uberbosses fer fun.<br>
But bar none , the grey shissars are the best.<br>
As for the wavecrasher.. well at 9/19 with a decent dex, you run a good chance to land a slow.and then switch weapons.<br>
<br>
I use a facesmasher , but as for good 1hs, jeldorin, hoarfroast hamer, darkmetal falchion, even the 19/25 one from veks is good.<br>
With instrument of nife,its the Chance to proc that 243 pt dd that is the killer. I find certain weapons seem to proc more then others.. very strange, but all those weapons above I own.<br>
I also suggest every palie get a tash stick.It can really , really useful.<br>
Me and Xerxus(60th cleric) once  killed a lvl 60 mob , all due to tashing it and landing roots.Damn thought destroyer took 20 min. but we dropped it.grats again finn on the ring.<br>
<br>
And palies get to know the location of XI thall. the 35 ac flowing cape is soo amazing.<br>
Here is how ya pull him.get a levitae and sow, stached behind a bunch a crap buffs.Move to the hill behind the area, and use a telescope to target him.<br>
next move beside the house on the water. levitated.<br>
